 <H1>Self-Organization of Orientation Maps, Lateral Connections, and
Dynamic Receptive Fields in the Primary Visual Cortex</H1>
<P><STRONG>
<!WA7><!WA7><!WA7><!WA7><!WA7><!WA7><!WA7><A NAME=tex2html9 HREF="http://www.cs.utexas.edu/users/sirosh">Joseph 
